definition: to reject/to discard/to get rid of
to scrape the meat from bones/to pick (teeth etc)/to weed out
to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including

sentences.english: It is better to weed out the bad businesses within the group rather than cross-subsidise them to save face.
sentences.chinese: 将集团内的不良业务剔除，好过为了面子予以挽救。

sentences.english: We always reject zero as an eigenfunction on the ground of physics.
sentences.chinese: 根据物理上的理由，我们总是剔除把零作为本征函数。

sentences.english: A new method for removing redundant points from 3D scattered point sets is presented.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种剔除空间散乱点集中冗余点的新方法。

sentences.english: May include meat trimmed from the blade and root portions of the tongue.
sentences.chinese: 可包括从舌叶和舌根部分剔除的肉。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate the clinical value of laparoscopic myomectomy .
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨腹腔镜下子宫肌瘤剔除术的临床应用价值。

sentences.english: A good organizational hierarchy can speed frustum and occlusion culling.
sentences.chinese: 一个好的结构可以加快视锥剔除和遮挡筛选。
开始剔除不必要的事情。

sentences.english: The film is to be cleaned up and re- edited.
sentences.chinese: 这部影片应剔除糟粕，重新进行剪辑。

sentences.english: In practice, what they do is take away some of the snobbery from education.
sentences.chinese: 实际上，他们所做的是从教育中剔除某些势利课程。

sentences.english: Were Reavers really taken out of the game?
sentences.chinese: 金甲虫真的从游戏里剔除了吗？

sentences.english: False edges due to truncation artifacts can be removed using this method.
sentences.chinese: 本方法可以有效地剔除由截断伪影而引入的虚假边缘。

sentences.english: There were multiple polypoid tissue in the bladder.
sentences.chinese: 剔除膀胱及输尿管周围多余脂肪组织。

sentences.english: Because of this, Rorty claims reserve Pragmatism and give up Empiricism.
sentences.chinese: 所以罗蒂主张保留实用主义而把经验主义加以剔除。

sentences.english: All remaining patches are culled against the viewing frustum .
sentences.chinese: 剩下的缀片通过视见体进行剔除。

sentences.english: The results of removing the extreme values were similar to those in data transformation.
sentences.chinese: 极值剔除后的热点辨析结果与数据转换后的结果类似。

sentences.english: Objective To evaluate the value of laparoscopic myomectomy in the treatment of myoma of uterus.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨腹腔镜下子宫肌瘤剔除术的技术处理特点。
